<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="26" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="5.[136,1452,157,976]" pageId="5" pageNumber="26">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,265,590,616]" pageId="5" pageNumber="26">Notes:</emphasis>
—1. The presence of 
<taxonomicName box="[509,668,590,616]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ericaceae" genus="Lyonia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="5" pageNumber="26" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="villosa">
<emphasis box="[509,668,590,616]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="26">Lyonia villosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<collectingCountry box="[704,799,590,616]" name="Vietnam" pageId="5" pageNumber="26">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
was indicated by 
<bibRefCitation author="Hiep, N. T. &amp; Ho, P. H." box="[1003,1213,590,617]" pageId="5" pageNumber="26" pagination="82 - 94" refId="ref6798" refString="Hiep, N. T. &amp; Ho, P. H. (1996) Fam. Ericaceae Juss. - Do quyen. In: Averyanov, L. V., Ban, N. T., Hiep, N. T. &amp; Loc, P. K. (Eds.) Vascular plants synopsis of Vietnamese flora. Vol. 2. Mir I Semya- 95, Saint Petersburg, pp. 82 - 94." type="book chapter" year="1996">Hiep &amp; Ho (1996)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Ho, P. H." box="[1225,1341,590,616]" pageId="5" pageNumber="26" refId="ref6881" refString="Ho, P. H. (1999) An illustrated flora of Vietnam. Vol. 1. Youth Publishing House, Ho Chi Minh City, 991 pp. [In Vietnamese]" type="book" year="1999">Ho (1999)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Hiep, N. T." pageId="5" pageNumber="26" pagination="1789" refId="ref6743" refString="Hiep, N. T. (2003) 83. Ericaceae Juss. 1789. In: Ban, N. T. (Ed.) Checklist of plant species in Vietnam. Vol. 2. Agriculture Publishing House, Hanoi, pp. 437 - 448. [In Vietnamese]" type="book chapter" year="2003">Hiep (2003)</bibRefCitation>
, but until now has not been confirmed by specimen citation. 
<bibRefCitation author="Ho, P. H." box="[923,1041,626,652]" pageId="5" pageNumber="26" refId="ref6881" refString="Ho, P. H. (1999) An illustrated flora of Vietnam. Vol. 1. Youth Publishing House, Ho Chi Minh City, 991 pp. [In Vietnamese]" type="book" year="1999">Ho (1999)</bibRefCitation>
reported the species to be found in Hoang Lien Son Mountain Range, apparently basing the report on the specimens 
<emphasis box="[1056,1199,662,688]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="26">Pételot 7986</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis box="[1255,1311,662,688]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="26">8021</emphasis>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Hiep, N. T. &amp; Ho, P. H." pageId="5" pageNumber="26" pagination="82 - 94" refId="ref6798" refString="Hiep, N. T. &amp; Ho, P. H. (1996) Fam. Ericaceae Juss. - Do quyen. In: Averyanov, L. V., Ban, N. T., Hiep, N. T. &amp; Loc, P. K. (Eds.) Vascular plants synopsis of Vietnamese flora. Vol. 2. Mir I Semya- 95, Saint Petersburg, pp. 82 - 94." type="book chapter" year="1996">Hiep &amp; Ho (1996)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Hiep, N. T." box="[266,402,698,724]" pageId="5" pageNumber="26" pagination="1789" refId="ref6743" refString="Hiep, N. T. (2003) 83. Ericaceae Juss. 1789. In: Ban, N. T. (Ed.) Checklist of plant species in Vietnam. Vol. 2. Agriculture Publishing House, Hanoi, pp. 437 - 448. [In Vietnamese]" type="book chapter" year="2003">Hiep (2003)</bibRefCitation>
listed 
<taxonomicName box="[478,582,698,724]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ericaceae" genus="Lyonia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="5" pageNumber="26" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="villosa">
<emphasis box="[478,582,698,724]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="26">L. villosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
for 
<collectingRegion box="[629,719,698,724]" country="Vietnam" name="Lao Cai" pageId="5" pageNumber="26">Lao Cai</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingRegion box="[774,881,698,724]" country="Vietnam" name="Kon Tum" pageId="5" pageNumber="26">Kon Tum</collectingRegion>
provinces; we were unable to trace any specimens of this species from 
<collectingRegion box="[363,474,734,760]" country="Vietnam" name="Kon Tum" pageId="5" pageNumber="26">Kon Tum</collectingRegion>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[136,1452,157,976]" pageId="5" pageNumber="26">
In addition, 
